                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-84-defend685 t18030914-84-punish493"></join>
               Transported for fourteen years
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Joseph Robinson, <rs id="t18030914-84-verdict494" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18030914-84-verdict494" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Le Blanc.</p>
